<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="ios_base" id="ios_base">ios_base</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="cpp code cpp"><span class="co2">#include &lt;ios&gt;</span>
&nbsp;
<span class="kw2">class</span> ios_base<span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
The class <code>ios_base</code> provides facilities for inspecting error state of the stream object. Character type independent formatting flags are stored here as well.
</p>

</div>

